# LACHESIS Plot Settings
# Format is property value

### GENERAL
figsize 12,8
fontsize 26
fontname serif
tick_labelsize 22

### CORNER PLOT
corner_fontsize 20
corner_tick_fontsize 15
corner_labelpad 15
corner_med_c firebrick
corner_med_style --
corner_v_c lightcoral
corner_v_style -.

### HR DIAGRAM
hr_figsize 12,8
hr_cmap cool
hr_marker *
hr_color greenyellow
